WEBVTT

00:01.877 --> 00:06.225
At close to 10 billion dollars, Line Corp was the biggest tech IPO of the year...

00:06.515 --> 00:09.105
...when it launched on the US market in 2016.

00:09.419 --> 00:14.891
It could be now joining forces to form a tech giant worth at a possible 27 billion dollars,...

00:15.167 --> 00:16.485
...nearly three times that.

00:16.866 --> 00:22.047
Discussions are underway between the messaging app operator and Z Holdings,...

00:22.281 --> 00:24.697
...known until last month as Yahoo Japan.

00:24.973 --> 00:28.755
The two would bring together Japan's biggest QR code payment apps,...

00:29.087 --> 00:32.888
...combining a potential customer base of 100 million users,...

00:33.141 --> 00:36.609
...if, at this point, Line's services are money-losing...

00:36.956 --> 00:40.038
...and nothing has been decided, it said, regarding a merger.

